{"tid":218421,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"綿戶亮跟朋友炫耀：「我跟新垣『那個』了唷！」","createTime":"2017-04-26T13:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T08:35:27.000Z","uid":4492,"like":20,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bbdef4b27ff83fb44e4e5b062e86ed1e28999781","tid":218421,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:16:34.000Z","msg":"傑尼斯「肉食偶像」錦戶亮今年3月被拍到「騎」進清純女星新垣結衣香閨，行事不但不低調，還驕傲地到處跟朋友炫耀：「我跟新垣『那個』了唷！」讓她形象大傷，上月10日已協議分手，戀情8個月玩完。 <br />\n<br />\n　錦戶亮與新垣結衣於2011年合作演出日劇《全開女孩》，當時並未擦出火花。拍完數月後，兩人在餐廳偶遇，才又恢復聯絡進而交往，新垣結衣還為愛遷徙，搬到離錦戶亮住處走路僅5分鐘的公寓；今年3月錦戶被拍到逕自出入她家大門，似乎擁有門禁卡，顯示感情穩定。 <br />\n<br />\n　身高172公分的新垣結衣當時被拍到夜會錦戶亮，獻出「緋聞處女秀」，但引起大批粉絲哀號，嫌她「眼光很差」。 <br />\n<br />\n　日本《週刊女性》還爆料，花邊新聞不斷的錦戶亮，多次在外跟朋友炫耀兩人的性關係，損害她的清純形象，讓新垣結衣非常受傷，決定斬草除根，趕在上月11日「光棍節」前夕提出分手，許多粉絲都表示「不意外」，還有網友說：「我還以為他們只是玩玩，沒想到能交往8個月。」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec3273ef7acaea5e8fef1e445e5dc9935ed4b63","tid":218421,"uid":1147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39351c7593d0ee4a17f716653d60dd8361c97120","tid":218421,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:18:37.000Z","msg":"死臭g"},{"pid":"a455650a65f13d85b325f91ba12a1d604e252e42","tid":218421,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:18:58.000Z","msg":"臭g"},{"pid":"bf5e05da2d6beb1f77998e47854693830c5e46fa","tid":218421,"uid":262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:20:20.000Z","msg":"Jeff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0b1c37dae6e3a92fbff51d40f27d6724f98ad8","tid":218421,"uid":34993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:25:07.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦<br />\n好多人捧GA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56ca59372e335936d747f8e37f8c1c2ce93b23d","tid":218421,"uid":66999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:26:09.000Z","msg":"趙完唱真係好乞人憎"},{"pid":"737ca0520d68cf03e4485d15cc8a8a7ea152b4a5","tid":218421,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"那個了唷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa05f5d87a727d51af39b1242834ab978afcd677","tid":218421,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"e766f89508d2d009c6ffd67b06e843bb6f6ff71d","tid":218421,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:27:27.000Z","msg":"結衣系雞"},{"pid":"0fec49eda07f1ded1ca67123f5875974b3507da6","tid":218421,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"fa3373d04cf3a698c473f19bcd6fa72d240cbb2f","tid":218421,"uid":25002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39e7f9ad8685783f27c3482cd5488efdb1c9bbca","tid":218421,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:28:12.000Z","msg":"就算係我都要屌😡😡😡"},{"pid":"d9881bfb666d38addf06c8e0046cd8d5eaab8533","tid":218421,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622a4ec7c738f66c5f6ebd407d74e4a566262632","tid":218421,"uid":12402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as